{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Ambush_of_Lando_Calrissian",
  "title": "The Trap Over Nar Shaddaa",
  "summary": "As Lando Calrissian's yacht the Lady Luck lifts off from Nar Shaddaa, a coordinated ambush springs around him: the Privateer Marauder corvette Harmattan under Dylan, the Black Sun crime lord Tyy'sun Eson, and the veteran Imperial Danik Kreldin in his Z-95A all converge to capture the New Republic hero alive. Outgunned and outnumbered, Lando weaves and returns fire in a desperate dogfight, dueling Danik and the Sullustan pilot Zero while the corvette's tractor beams and turbolasers hammer his shields. After enduring torpedo after torpedo, the Lady Luck is finally crippled and left lifeless in space, and the boarding party storms the battered yacht. Lando ambushes them from the shadows, gravely wounding Tyy'sun with shotgun fire before the Twi'lek's reckless charge draws him into the open. Danik's riot gun blast knocks Lando unconscious, and the captured hero is dragged toward the Harmattan's hangar and waiting bacta, the ambush a complete success.",
